            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&quot;&gt;﻿Future Contact Consent&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;If you would like us to contact you with regard to future roles or career initiatives which are relevant to your work history and may be of interest to you please tick the relevant boxes below.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;This would require us to hold some of your personal data on our candidate database, including your name, date of birth, contact details and work history.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, &amp;quot;Fira Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(23, 43, 77); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;For further details on how we use and store your data please review our &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.rssglobal.com/privacy-policy/&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(11, 92, 171); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;privacy notice&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;You can also unsubscribe at any time by contacting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; dpo@rssglobal.com.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Please check the boxes below to specify the form of contact you consent to:&lt